      "releaseNotes": "3 New Filters Added for November\nThis winter, create soft pink tones and cool selfies with these new filters.\n\n- jelly (jelly pop)\nA pink filter that gives your photos a cute and dreamy look, just like a pretty Instagram feed.\nEven tricky tones are easy to capture with just this filter.\n\n- jelly+ (jelly pop+)\nA softer version of the jelly filter.\nGreat for shooting cute indoor items, OOTD shots, or desserts.\n\n- winter (winter girl)\nBrings back the beloved tones of the popular “winter girl” selfie filter.\nOne filter is all you need to capture cool and bright winter selfies.",
